WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:00.866
Oh, dear.

2
00:00:00.866 --> 00:00:03.766
How dare I lie to you about Master Guan?

3
00:00:03.766 --> 00:00:06.000
Mr. Shen did cure Master Qin's illness

4
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.266
And it also solved my feng shui problem.

5
00:00:08.266 --> 00:00:09.566
He is not only proficient in medicine

6
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:11.666
Feng Shui is a must.

7
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:14.166
Not learning well at a young age

8
00:00:14.166 --> 00:00:16.966
But fooling around with the Qin family's dog

9
00:00:16.966 --> 00:00:19.500
Du Yuanhua who wants to deceive the old man

10
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:22.866
The old man kept the Du Yuan flower to save his life

11
00:00:22.866 --> 00:00:26.066
Don't think I'm dim-eyed, anyone can lie to you

12
00:00:26.066 --> 00:00:28.600
Love Tainen, get out of here

13
00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:31.500
My dad might as well let him try

14
00:00:33.766 --> 00:00:35.366
The feng shui in this room was done by me

15
00:00:35.366 --> 00:00:36.300
Don't report it.

16
00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:39.233
What I said doesn't work anymore, does it?

17
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:41.900
Dad, I didn't mean that

18
00:00:42.166 --> 00:00:44.500
Boy, get out of here

19
00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:47.300
Otherwise, old man, I'm going to get moldy

20
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:54.133
Duan Lao, if I guessed correctly

21
00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:57.166
Your back gets cold every night.

22
00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:59.133
I couldn't sleep all night.

23
00:00:59.133 --> 00:01:01.266
Sleeping during the day is also a nightmare

24
00:01:01.266 --> 00:01:02.900
For less than an hour at a time

25
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.266
The thief is expensive, and you told him all these things.

26
00:01:06.266 --> 00:01:08.500
But you investigated it clearly

27
00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:10.800
I dare to come here and pretend to be a ghost

